# Livia surfaces cascade

Policy is the hub (`lib/policy` → API → thin `artifacts/*`). Do not fix one surface in isolation when the flow is shared.

## If you touched…

| Area | Also check |
|------|------------|
| Dashboard UI / copy | Mobile equivalent; marketing only if public-facing message |
| Mobile screen | Web parity or intentional web-only doc |
| Marketing (livia.io) | Scroll-to-top on route change; pricing matches business docs |
| Internal ops | `INTERNAL_OPS_SECRET`; support registry |
| Public `/b` guest | All verticals with same pattern — policy guest surfaces |
| Gateway G1–G3 / sign-in | `docs/design/assets/w2-gateway/**/*.target.png`; screen cards |
| Demo provision | Demo slugs, Clerk sync, `/demo` path |
| API / OpenAPI | `pnpm codegen` — never hand-edit generated clients |

## Ports (local full stack)

- API `3000` · dashboard `5173` · marketing `5174` · internal `5175`

